  {
   "id": "opt_txt",
   "type": "text",
   "x": 1770,
   "y": 1345,
   "width": 945.0,
   "height": 150.0,
   "angle": 0,
   "strokeColor": "#2b8a3e",
   "backgroundColor": "transparent",
   "fillStyle": "solid",
   "strokeWidth": 2,
   "strokeStyle": "solid",
   "roughness": 1,
   "opacity": 100,
   "groupIds": [],
   "frameId": null,
   "roundness": null,
   "seed": 1363383345,
   "version": 1,
   "versionNonce": 1289537409,
   "isDeleted": false,
   "boundElements": [],
   "updated": 1,
   "link": null,
   "locked": false,
   "text": "1. MODEL ROUTING \u2014 cheap (green) for classify/summarize/clarify/screens, mid (orange) for extract/stories\n2. PROMPT CACHING-READY \u2014 every system prompt static; 90% off on Anthropic cache hits\n3. NON-BLOCKING/BATCH \u2014 all generation via BackgroundTasks \u2192 Batch API in production (-50%)\n4. STRUCTURED JSON + max_tokens caps \u2014 models fill fields, never narrate (-40% output)\n\nPlus: content-hash gates (yellow) \u00b7 map-reduce (summaries only to 70B) \u00b7 titles-only epics (-77%)\nper-epic scoped stories (-85%) \u00b7 rule-based constraint injection (0 LLM) \u00b7 Jaccard dedup\nsummaries-only RAG \u00b7 RRF + top-5 rerank gate  \u21d2  ~87% measured savings vs naive Opus",
   "fontSize": 15,
   "fontFamily": 1,
   "textAlign": "left",
   "verticalAlign": "top",
   "containerId": null,
   "originalText": "1. MODEL ROUTING \u2014 cheap (green) for classify/summarize/clarify/screens, mid (orange) for extract/stories\n2. PROMPT CACHING-READY \u2014 every system prompt static; 90% off on Anthropic cache hits\n3. NON-BLOCKING/BATCH \u2014 all generation via BackgroundTasks \u2192 Batch API in production (-50%)\n4. STRUCTURED JSON + max_tokens caps \u2014 models fill fields, never narrate (-40% output)\n\nPlus: content-hash gates (yellow) \u00b7 map-reduce (summaries only to 70B) \u00b7 titles-only epics (-77%)\nper-epic scoped stories (-85%) \u00b7 rule-based constraint injection (0 LLM) \u00b7 Jaccard dedup\nsummaries-only RAG \u00b7 RRF + top-5 rerank gate  \u21d2  ~87% measured savings vs naive Opus",
   "lineHeight": 1.25,
   "baseline": 146.0
  },
  {
